data.AUTH0_CALLBACK_URL: Auth0 callback URL for this app, must be authorized on the Auth0 dashboard
data.AUTH0_CLIENT_ID: Auth0 client ID for this app, from the Auth0 dashboard
data.AUTH0_CLIENT_SECRET: Auth0 client secret for this app, from the Auth0 dashboard
data.AUTH0_DOMAIN: Auth0 domain for this app, from the Auth0 dashboard
data.DEBUG: Value for the `DEBUG` environment variable; see https://www.npmjs.com/package/debug
data.SESSION_SECRET: Absolute path to the .key file for signing session cookies
data.SSL_CERT: Absolute path to the server.crt file
